
1. Planning Goals
2. Develop and Design

1. Create github Project
2. Clone Project in local machine

git clone git@github.com:jesusalc/jobboard.git

3. Generate Rails Files

rails new jobboard


4. Init First Git Push

cd jobboard

git config user.name "Jesus Alcaras"
git config user.email "jesusalc@gmail.com"

git add . 
git commit -m "Rails New"
git push -u origin master

