bundle install


6. Generate Tables Scaffold

rails g scaffold job title:string description:text company_name:string details_link:string

rake db:create
rake db:migrate

git add . 
git commit -m "Generate Scaffold Title Descripcion Company Name Details Link"
git push -u origin master


7. Fix app/views/layout/application.html.erb convert to Haml if haml is desired. 

*Rails will see .erb first than .haml files if both are left in the folder



